Fronton was first listed as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/> Prior to the [[2010 U.S. census]], three new CDPs were carved out from its territory ([[Guadalupe-Guerra, Texas|Guadalupe-Guerra]], [[Sandoval, Texas|Sandoval]], [[Sunset, Starr County, Texas|Sunset]]) substantially reducing its population.<ref name=2010CensusTX/>

